<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Calico on Utop's Blog</title><link>https://www.ffutop.com/tags/calico/</link><description>Recent content in Calico on Utop's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cmn-Hans-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2019 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ffutop.com/tags/calico/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Calico 网络通信解析</title><link>https://www.ffutop.com/posts/2019-12-24-how-calico-works/</link><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.ffutop.com/posts/2019-12-24-how-calico-works/</guid><description>&lt;p>在 Kubernetes 集群中，Calico 区别于 Flannel 的最显著特征，就是其宣称可以不借助隧道技术，是建立在纯三层协议上的解决方案。也就是说，Calico 通过建立一些路由信息，就构建了单节点/多节点网络命名空间隔离下的通信网络。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>